<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Cookie Policy - NextScrimz</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #ffe69b;
        --primary-dark: rgb(149, 123, 74);
        --color-dark: #161616;
        --secondary: #00cec9;
        --dark: #2d3436;
        --light: #f7f9fc;
        --success: #00b894;
        --warning: #fdcb6e;
        --danger: #e17055;
        --nav-height: 80px;
        --border-radius: 8px;
        --box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        --transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--dark);
        background-color: var(--light);
      }

      .container {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }
      /* Main Content Styles */
      .cookie-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-dark) 0%, #2a2a3a 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 4rem 0;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }

      .cookie-hero h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--primary);
      }

      .cookie-hero p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .cookie-content {
        padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
      }

      .policy-section {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .policy-section:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .policy-section h3 {
        color: var(--primary-dark);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .policy-section h3 span {
        margin-right: 10px;
        background-color: var(--primary);
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .policy-section p,
      .policy-section ul {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .policy-section ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
      }

      .policy-section li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .cookie-types {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }

      .cookie-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        border-top: 4px solid var(--primary);
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .cookie-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .cookie-card h4 {
        color: var(--primary-dark);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .cookie-card h4 i {
        margin-right: 10px;
        color: var(--primary-dark);
      }

      .cookie-card.essential {
        border-top-color: var(--success);
      }

      .cookie-card.performance {
        border-top-color: var(--secondary);
      }

      .cookie-card.preference {
        border-top-color: var(--warning);
      }

      .cookie-card.advertising {
        border-top-color: var(--danger);
      }

      .highlight {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .note-box {
        background-color: rgba(253, 203, 110, 0.2);
        border-left: 4px solid var(--warning);
        padding: 1rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }

      /* Responsive Styles */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .header-content {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }

        nav ul {
          margin-top: 1rem;
          justify-content: center;
        }

        nav ul li {
          margin: 0 0.5rem;
        }

        .cookie-hero h2 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .cookie-types {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .logo h1 {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .cookie-hero {
          padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .cookie-hero h2 {
          font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .policy-section {
          padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .policy-section h3 {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./header-footer/header') %>

    <section class="cookie-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Cookie Policy</h2>
        <p>
          This policy explains how NextScrimz uses cookies and similar
          technologies to enhance your experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cookie-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>1</span> What Are Cookies?</h3>
          <p>
            Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you
            visit a website. They help us recognize your device, remember your
            preferences, and improve your experience.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>2</span> Types of Cookies We Use</h3>
          <p>We use different types of cookies for various purposes:</p>

          <div class="cookie-types">
            <div class="cookie-card essential">
              <h4><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Essential Cookies</h4>
              <p>
                Required for the website to function (e.g., login, account
                authentication, security features). Without these, some services
                cannot be provided.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cookie-card performance">
              <h4>
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Performance & Analytics
                Cookies
              </h4>
              <p>
                Help us understand how users interact with NextScrimz by
                collecting information such as page visits, time spent, and
                error reports.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cookie-card preference">
              <h4><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Preference Cookies</h4>
              <p>
                Store your settings (e.g., language, dark/light theme, room
                filters) so you don't have to reset them each time you visit.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cookie-card advertising">
              <h4><i class="fas fa-ad"></i> Advertising & Marketing Cookies</h4>
              <p>
                May be used to show relevant promotions or tournament offers.
                These will only be enabled with your consent.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>3</span> How We Use Cookies</h3>
          <p>We use cookies to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Keep you logged in securely.</li>
            <li>Save your preferences and custom settings.</li>
            <li>Analyze site traffic and improve performance.</li>
            <li>Detect and prevent fraudulent activities.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>4</span> Third-Party Cookies</h3>
          <p>
            Some cookies may be set by third-party services integrated into
            NextScrimz, such as:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Payment providers (e.g., Razorpay) to ensure secure transactions.
            </li>
            <li>
              Analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics) for performance tracking.
            </li>
            <li>
              Hosting/CDN services for faster and secure content delivery.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="note-box">
            <p>
              We do not control third-party cookies and recommend reviewing
              their policies.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>5</span> Managing Cookies</h3>
          <p>
            You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings.
            However, please note:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Disabling essential cookies may affect the functionality of
              NextScrimz.
            </li>
            <li>
              You may not be able to participate in events or log in properly if
              cookies are blocked.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>6</span> Updates to This Policy</h3>
          <p>
            We may update this Cookie Policy occasionally. Any changes will be
            posted on this page with a new effective date.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h3><span>7</span> Contact Us</h3>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact
            us:
          </p>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
            <span>Email: support@nextscrimz.com</span>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
            <span>Website: nextscrimz.com</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('./header-footer/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
